description: Variation of Condition 2 of approved planning permission 5211/18: increase height of hay barn by 2.5m and relocation of isolation unit to be located in the paddock adjacent to the cottages at the end of Fox Burrow Road. (AMENDED DESCRIPTION AND PLANS). (Summary).
site_name: Development At Hainault Forest Country Park And Foxburrows Farm
decision_conditions:
The development hereby permitted shall be begun no later than the  expiration of three years from the date of 01-May-2019.

Reason: In order to comply with the requirements of Section 91 of the Town and Country Planning Act 1990.
